Package org.transitime.worldbank.gtfsRtExample

For helping transit agencies provide a GTFS-realtime feed of their GPS data by querying a database and putting the data into GTFS-realtime format.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigurableParameters
    Parameters that need to be configured for the individual transit agency.
    DataFetcher
    For retrieving ApiVehicle from the database
    GtfsRealtimeExample
    For processing GPS data and outputting it into a GTFS-realtime format file.
    VehicleData
    For keeping data from the database.
